---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="关于">
  <h1 class="page-title">
    <span data-lang="zh">关于</span>
    <span data-lang="en">About</span>
  </h1>
  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      <span data-lang="zh">写代码的人，也写字。</span>
      <span data-lang="en">A person who writes code, and also writes.</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span data-lang="zh">
        这里没有简历，没有头衔，只有一些想法落地的地方——
        有时候是一段能跑起来的程序，有时候只是一句话。
      </span>
      <span data-lang="en">
        No résumé here, no titles — just a place where ideas land, sometimes
        as a program that runs, sometimes as a single sentence.
      </span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span data-lang="zh">欢迎路过，欢迎留言。</span>
      <span data-lang="en">Glad you stopped by. Feel free to leave a comment.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
